This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new framework for training GANs and discusses the theoretical improvement in generalization ability. The paper also focuses on image generation tasks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of regularizers and constraints, which are common in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the manipulation of weight matrices, which could also fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
